            . The Prosecutor depos'd, That he lost the Horse from Grass about Christmas last, and that he afterwards stealing a Horse something like his, he fell in Discount with the Person who rode on it, who said he was going to New-Prison, to speak with a Prisoner who could very likely give an Account of it, for he was in Trouble about a Horse; accordingly that Person whose Name in 
